                A car starts from rest and accelerates to a velocity of <m>40 \textbf{ m/s}</m> in <m>10 \textbf{ seconds}</m> . It then maintains this velocity for <m>15 \textbf{ seconds}</m> before decelerating to rest, with the total time of motion being <m>45 \textbf{ seconds}</m>
            </p>
            <p>
